## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification (Browser)

1. Start backend: run `python app.py` in `d:\crop project\backend`.
2. Open `d:\crop project\frontend\index.html` in a browser.
3. Go to **Recommend** page → fill location + soil type → click **Analyse & Recommend**.
4. Verify the crop selector section appears below results, showing 5 crops (1 best + 4 related).
5. Click **"Select"** on any crop — verify it highlights green and a toast appears.
6. Navigate to **Weather** page — verify the **4-Day Water Schedule** panel appears with 4 date cards showing `recommended_water_L` values.
7. Go to **History** page — verify the chosen crop appears as a tag on the latest history card.
